subject: Basketball (College)
organizations: Rutgers, The State University of New Jersey
lead_paragraph: C. Vivian Stringer became the fourth N.C.A.A. women’s college basketball coach to reach 900 wins as host Rutgers cruised past South Florida, 68-56.
